package main

import (
	"github.com/gorilla/mux"
	"net/http"
)

// UriInterface is interface for /uri root endpoint
type UriInterface interface { // Users_idGet is the handler for GET /uri/{users-id}
	Users_idGet(http.ResponseWriter, *http.Request)
}

// UriInterfaceRoutes is routing for /uri root endpoint
func UriInterfaceRoutes(r *mux.Router, i UriInterface) {
	r.HandleFunc("/uri/{users-id}", i.Users_idGet).Methods("GET")
}
